      {
        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "Provisional Junior Councillors (gon-shō-sanji) — a long named roster beginning with Konami Gorō and continuing across the next pages (p163 left / p164). It includes future national figures such as Kataoka Kenkichi and Tani Tateki (谷干城). The roster's 海陸兵員 ('sea-and-land troops') total of 9,000 prints on p164 — the same force shown on the demographics page as 常備兵 6,600 + 非常兵 2,400."
